executionArgs.additionalInstruction: The dev server is running on port 3000. Test user credentials: student_id=S12345, password=secret. The test user has integration tokens for both notion and google_calendar. Custom auth endpoint at /api/auth/signin/credentials accepts POST with {student_id, password}. Admin stats endpoint requires header x-admin-secret: ADMIN_SECRET. Prerequisites: course PREFIXnnn where nnn>101 requires PREFIX+(nnn-1) to be completed. Progress save body format: {major, completed} where completed is array of objects with code property.
